{"tid":1884474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強力建議RTHK成立監驚會","createTime":"2020-02-17T15:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T05:20:51.000Z","uid":117622,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9b0e80d5b9b444c1e10b8caf03bf326b0efff4","tid":1884474,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:16:04.000Z","msg":"我建議監驚會係一個獨立機構<br />\n其職係觀察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />監察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />覆檢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以頭條新聞監製匯報調查工作<br />\n<br />\n監驚會應該由一名主席、三名副主席和不少於八名委員組成<br />\n委員全部應該由頭條新聞監製委任<br />\n分別來自RTHK不同成員組成<br />\n包括製作人、主持人、演員等<br />\n監驚會應借助委員多方面的專業知識<br />\n獨立<br />\n公正<br />\n透徹<br />\n監察投訴RTHK調查工作<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8bdf5e90a477dcafafe9af24273c0db86076fb","tid":1884474,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:45:43.000Z","msg":"好似有人投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c55b4323cd83ee9d84fb97b6f3611781ce3b85","tid":1884474,"uid":273703,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:46:55.000Z","msg":"應成立 港台投訴科，自己人查自己人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822153b6de31b741ec75061f23fd50128af87f61","tid":1884474,"uid":175346,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:47:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8c66018c291240fd6bccfe779cb4cdd99305a2c","tid":1884474,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:47:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5377a5380a74e8b23a5dd2f2b1d93094cc9631f","tid":1884474,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:48:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f32399ac8f7f8861ddd0eee87d3a87da1f1f